       <h4>Young Alumna to Serve World Concern in Burma</h4> 
       <div class="content"> 
        <p><a href="http://blogs.westmont.edu/2014/10/16/young-alumna-to-serve-world-concern-in-burma/"><img src="http://blogs.westmont.edu/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/madagascar1-of-2-168x168-1413496231.jpg" width="84" height="84" alt="Taylor Jashinsky in Madagascar"></a><span class="text">Taylor Jashinsky ’14 will serve as a communications liaison for the next two years in Southern Asia with World Concern, a Christian non-profit committed to developing sustainable communities in poverty stricken areas around the world. </span> <a href="http://blogs.westmont.edu/2014/10/16/young-alumna-to-serve-world-concern-in-burma/">[more]</a></p> 
